    <a name=basics></a>
    <h3>Project Basics</h3>

    This project is aimed at using an swap file on our Linux systems. We want
    to be able to generate an RAM size dependant swap file in /var.
    <p>
    This project has produced an <a href="dphys-swapfile">dphys-swapfile</a>
    script for sizing, setting up and mounting an swap file. And an
    <a href="debian/dphys-swapfile.init">init.d script</a> that runs this
    script, together with an Debian packaging of the whole lot.
    <p>
    This project was spawned from the
    <a href="http://www.phys.ethz.ch/~franklin/Projects/dphys2/">dphys2
    project</a>.


